                <span><strong class="text-brand-text">Per-bag pricing</strong> option available</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-brand-primary mr-2 font-bold">‚úì</span>
                <span><strong class="text-brand-text">Priority scheduling</strong> - get first pick of time slots</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-brand-primary mr-2 font-bold">‚úì</span>
                <span><strong class="text-brand-text">One free rush service per month</strong> ($10 value)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-brand-primary mr-2 font-bold">‚úì</span>
                <span>Free branded laundry bag</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-brand-primary mr-2 font-bold">‚úì</span>
