            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">1.</span>
              <span>We pick up your laundry at your door</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">2.</span>
              <span>Your items are weighed at our facility</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">3.</span>
              <span>You're charged $2.25 per pound (minimum $35)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">4.</span>
              <span>Clean, folded laundry delivered back to you</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The $35 minimum helps cover pickup & delivery costs for smaller loads. Most customers exceed this with a typical week's laundry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* COMMERCIAL PRICING */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-brand-bg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-start">

          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title text-brand-text mb-4 sm:mb-6">Commercial pricing</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
