              </table>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3 sm:mt-4">Final pricing depends on mix (towels/linens), bagging, and turnaround needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FAQ */}
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center text-brand-text mb-8 sm:mb-12">Pricing FAQ</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">How does membership work?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">Members get $1.99/lb pricing (vs $2.25/lb standard) and unlock per-bag pricing options. Choose your preferred pricing method for each order.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-brand-text mb-2 sm:mb-3">Can non-members use bag pricing?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm sm:text-base">Bag pricing is a members-only feature. Non-members can use our simple per-pound pricing at $2.25/lb with no membership required.</p>
